    <item>
      <title>[입에 착착 붙는 일본어] ~덕분에</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/nie/japanese/2025/01/10/VG7ODIYVO5DBTKPJOBVQ6ZCUKE/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/nie/japanese/2025/01/10/VG7ODIYVO5DBTKPJOBVQ6ZCUKE/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
